beIN SPORTS 1.original_title: Lamine Yamal - The Future Of Football
beIN SPORTS 1.title: لامين يامال - مستقبل كرة القدم
beIN SPORTS 1.desc: لامين يامال، معجزة تطورت في لا ماسيا، ارتقى في سن مبكرة إلى المسرح العالمي لكرة القدم بفضل موهبته ونضجه وإبداعه.
beIN SPORTS 1.title_fr: Lamine Yamal - L'avenir du football
beIN SPORTS 1.desc_en: Lamine Yamal, a prodigy developed at La Masia, has risen at a remarkably young age to the world stage of football thanks to his talent, maturity and creativity. Through his rapid ascent, this documentary asks a key question : is he just an early phenomenon, or true embodiment of the future of modern football ?
beIN SPORTS 1.desc_fr: Lamine Yamal, prodige développé à La Masia, s'est hissé très jeune sur la scène mondiale du football grâce à son talent, sa maturité et sa créativité.

beIN SPORTS 1.original_title: Barcelona vs Copenhagen - UEFA Champions League 2025/26 - MD8 - Mini Match
beIN SPORTS 1.title: برشلونة vs كوبنهاجن - دوري أبطال أوروبا 2025/26 - MD8 - مباراة صغيرة
beIN SPORTS 1.desc: اللقاءان الوحيدان السابقان بين برشلونة وكوبنهاغن جاءا في دور المجموعات من دوري أبطال أوروبا 2010-11، فاز برشلونة 2-0 في المباراة التي أقيمت على أرضه بفضل ثنائية ليونيل ميسي، قبل التعادل 1-1 في مباراة الإياب في الدنمارك.
beIN SPORTS 1.title_fr: Barcelone vs Copenhague - UEFA Champions League 2025/26 - MD8 - Mini Match
beIN SPORTS 1.desc_en: Barcelona and Copenhagen’s only two previous meetings came in the group stage of the 2010-11 UEFA Champions League – Barcelona won 2-0 in the home fixture thanks to a Lionel Messi brace, before drawing 1-1 in the reverse fixture in Denmark. Copenhagen didn’t win any of their first 15 matches against Spanish teams in European competition, yet won their most recent one, versus Villarreal on MD6 of this season’s UEFA Champions League.
beIN SPORTS 1.desc_fr: Les deux seules rencontres précédentes entre Barcelone et Copenhague ont eu lieu lors de la phase de groupes de l'UEFA Champions League 2010-11 – Barcelone s'est imposé 2-0 à domicile grâce à un doublé de Lionel Messi, avant de faire match nul 1-1 lors du match inverse au Danemark.

beIN SPORTS 1.title_fr: Liverpool vs Karabakh - UEFA Champions League 2025/26 - MD8 - Mini Match
beIN SPORTS 1.desc_en: Liverpool and Qarabag will meet for the first time in European competition – all three previous meetings between sides from England and Azerbaijan in the UEFA Champions League have been between Qarabag and Chelsea. Qarabag lost seven of their first eight meetings with English sides in Europe, but they did avoid defeat in the most recent one in the UEFA Champions League this season.
beIN SPORTS 1.desc_fr: Liverpool et Qarabag se rencontreront pour la première fois en compétition européenne – les trois précédentes rencontres entre des équipes d'Angleterre et d'Azerbaïdjan en UEFA Champions League ont eu lieu entre Qarabag et Chelsea.

beIN SPORTS 1.original_title: Paris Saint-Germain vs Newcastle United - UEFA Champions League 2025/26 - MD8 - Mini Match
beIN SPORTS 1.title: باريس سان جيرمان vs نيوكاسل يونايتد - دوري أبطال أوروبا 2025/26 - MD8 - مباراة صغيرة
beIN SPORTS 1.desc: اللقاء الوحيد السابق بين باريس سان جيرمان ونيوكاسل جاء في دوري أبطال أوروبا 2023-24، حيث تعادل الفريقان في بارك دي برينس، بعد فوز فريق إدي هاو بنتيجة 4-1 في المباراة الأولى على ملعب سانت جيمس بارك.
beIN SPORTS 1.title_fr: Paris Saint-Germain vs Newcastle United - UEFA Champions League 2025/26 - MD8 - Mini Match
beIN SPORTS 1.desc_en: Paris SG and Newcastle’s only previous meetings came in the 2023-24 UEFA Champions League – the two sides drew their meeting at the Parc des Princes, after Eddie Howe’s side had won 4-1 in the first game at St. James’ Park. This will be Newcastle’s 10th away game against a French side in Europe, while they have only managed one victory from the previous nine : 4-0 v Sochaux in the UEFA Cup in November 2004.
beIN SPORTS 1.desc_fr: Les seules rencontres précédentes du Paris SG et de Newcastle ont eu lieu lors de l’UEFA Champions League 2023-24 – les deux équipes ont fait match nul au Parc des Princes, après que l’équipe d’Eddie Howe ait gagné 4-1 lors du premier match à St. James’ Park.

beIN SPORTS 1.original_title: Benfica vs Real Madrid - UEFA Champions League 2025/26 - MD8 - Mini Match
beIN SPORTS 1.title: بنفيكا vs ريال مدريد - دوري أبطال أوروبا 2025/26 - MD8 - مباراة صغيرة
beIN SPORTS 1.desc: على الرغم من وجود 792 مباراة في كأس أوروبا/دوري أبطال أوروبا فيما بينها، إلا أن هذه الفرق التقت ثلاث مرات فقط في المسابقتين، وليس منذ ربع نهائي موسم 1964-1965.
beIN SPORTS 1.title_fr: Benfica vs Real Madrid - UEFA Champions League 2025/26 - MD8 - Mini Match
beIN SPORTS 1.desc_en: Despite having a combined 792 European Cup/UEFA Champions League matches between them, these teams have only met three times across the two competitions, and not since the 1964-65 quarter-finals.  Benfica have won two of the previous three meetings between themselves and Real Madrid, while their one defeat came in the second leg of the 1964-65 quarter-finals ; a tie they still progressed from 6-3 on aggregate.
beIN SPORTS 1.desc_fr: Malgré un total de 792 matches de Coupe d'Europe et d'UEFA Champions League, ces équipes ne se sont rencontrées que trois fois dans les deux compétitions, et pas depuis les quarts de finale de 1964-65.

beIN 4K.title_fr: Tottenham Hotspur contre Manchester City - Premier League anglaise 2026/2027
beIN 4K.desc_en: Tottenham have completed the Premier League double over Manchester City nine times so far, more than they have any other opponent. Meanwhile, only Chelsea  have done so more against the Citizens. Man City have won their last two away league games against Spurs, last winning three in a row between February 1973 and August 1974.
beIN 4K.desc_fr: Tottenham a réalisé le doublé en Premier League contre Manchester City neuf fois jusqu'à présent, plus que tout autre adversaire.

beIN 4K.original_title: Liverpool vs. Newcastle United - English Premier League 2026/2027
beIN 4K.title: ليفربول vs نيوكاسل يونايتد - الدوري الإنجليزي الممتاز 2026/2027
beIN 4K.desc: لم يخسر ليفربول في آخر 18 مباراة في الدوري الإنجليزي الممتاز ضد نيوكاسل، منذ الخسارة 2-0 خارج أرضه في ديسمبر 2015. فشل نيوكاسل في الفوز بأي من آخر 29 مباراة خارج أرضه في الدوري الإنجليزي الممتاز ضد ليفربول، وهي أطول فترة بدون فوز ضد خصم في تاريخ الدوري.
beIN 4K.title_fr: Liverpool contre Newcastle United - Premier League anglaise 2026/2027
beIN 4K.desc_en: Liverpool are unbeaten in their last 18 Premier League games against Newcastle, since a 2-0 away loss in December 2015. Newcastle have failed to win any of their last 29 Premier League away games against Liverpool, their joint-longest winless run against an opponent in their league history.
beIN 4K.desc_fr: Liverpool est invaincu lors de ses 18 derniers matchs de Premier League contre Newcastle, depuis une défaite 2-0 à l'extérieur en décembre 2015. Newcastle n'a remporté aucun de ses 29 derniers matchs à l'extérieur de Premier League contre Liverpool, sa plus longue série sans victoire contre un adversaire de son histoire en championnat.

beIN SPORTS EN 2.desc: هذا الشهر في برنامج روح الرياضة، يعيدنا جود بيلينجهام، لاعب كرة القدم في ريال مدريد وإنجلترا، إلى بداية رحلته في برمنجهام ويتحدث بصراحة عن صحته العقلية.
beIN SPORTS EN 2.desc_en: This month on Spirit of Sport, Real Madrid and England footballer Jude Bellingham takes us back to the start of his journey in Birmingham and opens up about his mental health. Ahead of the 2026 Winter Olympics in Milano Cortina, freestyle skier Eileen Gu reflects on her journey to gold. Cricket legend Sachin Tendulkar and tennis icon Novak Djokovic spotlight the transformative power of sport and how they’re using their platforms to give back. England Lioness Georgia Stanway visits a special football project in London to inspire the next generation.
beIN SPORTS EN 2.desc_fr: Ce mois-ci, dans Spirit of Sport, le footballeur du Real Madrid et de l'Angleterre Jude Bellingham nous ramène au début de son voyage à Birmingham et parle de sa santé mentale.

beIN SPORTS 3.title_fr: Borussia Dortmund vs Internazionale Milano - UEFA Champions League 2025/26 - MD8
beIN SPORTS 3.desc_en: Borussia Dortmund and Internazionale have faced each other on six previous occasions in Europe, with the most frequent result being an Inter victory. The last meeting between Borussia Dortmund and Internazionale was a 3-2 victory for the German side in November 2019 – a game that Inter led 2-0 in at half time. This remains the only time that Dortmund have trailed by 2+ goals at half time of a European Cup/UEFA Champions League game and gone on to win, as well as the only time Inter have led by 2+ goals at the break and lost in those competitions.

beIN SPORTS 3.title_fr: Lille vs Fribourg - UEFA Europa League 2025/2026 - MD8

Freiburg have won four of their five UEFA Europa League matches against French teams, including a 3-1 win over Nice earlier this season.

beIN SPORTS 3.title_fr: Panathinaikos vs Roma - UEFA Europa League 2025/2026 - MD8
